  "general_provisions": "This bill creates a new section in the Utah Construction Trades Licensing Act governing radon mitigation.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>requires a person that installs, repairs, maintains, cleans, or replaces a radon mitigation system to complete training and certification;<hr><ltbullet>requires an individual who sells radon mitigation or vents a radon mitigation system to complete training and certification;<hr><ltbullet>requires an employer to ensure that an employee performing radon mitigation work obtains required training and certification before performing that work; and<hr><ltbullet>authorizes the division to exempt an individual from certification requirements if the individual works under direct one-to-one supervision of a certified professional.",
